			<td class="foswikiTableCol1 foswikiSortedAscendingCol foswikiSortedCol" rowspan="1"> sort categories on each step of the hierarchy according to the given property; possible values: <code>order</code>, <code>name</code>, <code>title</code>, <code>ordertitle</code>;           <code>order</code> refers to the Order formfield of a category that can be used to influence sorting manually;           sorting categories by <code>order</code> ignores their lexical order as would be the case using <code>title</code>;           sorting by <code>ordertitle</code> first reads the Order property of a category and then falls back to lexical order </td>
			<td class="foswikiTableCol2 foswikiLastCol" rowspan="1"> <code>ordertitle</code> </td>
